## Phase 7: Academic Core Schema (NEW SYSTEM)
### Database Schema
- [x] Academic Sessions table (2023-24, 2024-25, etc.)
- [x] Programs table (EMGC, XRAY, PHARM, HOSP)
- [x] Semesters table (semester structure per program)
- [x] Subjects table (individual courses)
- [x] Program-Semester-Subject mapping (curriculum)
- [x] Subject-Teacher Assignment (RBAC enforcement)
- [x] Student Enrollment (lifecycle tracking)
- [x] Semester Progression Log (immutable audit)

### API Endpoints
- [x] `GET /admin/academic/sessions` - List sessions
- [x] `POST /admin/academic/sessions` - Create session
- [x] `GET /admin/academic/programs` - List programs
- [x] `POST /admin/academic/programs` - Create program
- [x] `POST /admin/academic/programs/{id}/enroll-student` - Enroll student
- [x] `GET /student/academic/enrollment` - My enrollment details
- [x] `GET /student/academic/transcript` - My academic history

